reviewText: The monster was OK,But like every P.C. movie these days,the Viking spirit was alive & well in the chick. The men were pretty candy. It had some good shots of Norway.

So many unusual reasons to love it! My favorite is that the male and female leads are about the same age. Then there's Norwegian. And special effects. And the freakishness of a baby midgard serpent. Why not five stars? No Fenrir.
